HEADWORD: Misuser
<hw>Mis*us"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
misuses.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Wretched <xex>misusers</xex> of language.⟦rdquo⟧
