<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>Unlawful use of a right; use in
excess of, or varying from, one's right.</def>
<rj><au>Bouvier.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

